<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l9">ʒu Aſchaffemburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_419_r1l10"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vıcʒtum / als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt . des Strölın </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l11">Juden hab bey vns / das geleyt daʒ wır vor geben <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu erlengen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l12">bıs auf <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> frawen tag lıechtmeſſ ſchıerıſt etc . das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l13"><expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd wellen das <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒulıeb tun . VVır <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l14"><expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſʒ . mıt <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Strölın Juden ʒu <expan>beſtelle<ex>n</ex></expan> . daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l15">er ſein ſache <expan>daʒwıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> alſo awſʒtrag / daʒ wır des darnach ver = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l16">tragen ſeyn . wan vns ſölıch ſache nıht wol füklıch ſein als Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l17">ſelbs wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> mugt / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_line_1577282828636_6646">etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_419" id="208v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Dieth<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Lantschad<ex>en</ex></expan>, vicztum zu Aschaffemburg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vicztum, als ir uns
                                                  <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt, des Strölin
                                                juden hab bey uns das geleyt, daz wir vor geben
                                          <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, zu erlengen bis auf <app><note><q type="date"><expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frawen tag
                                            liechtmess schierist </q>02.02.1423</note></app>
                                                  etc., das
                                                  <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol
                                                  <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>, und wellen das
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> zulieb tun. Wir
                                                  <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> ewr
                                                  <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleisz, mit
                                                  <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan> Strölin juden zu
                                                  <expan>bestelle<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz er sein
                                                sache <expan>dazwische<ex>n</ex></expan> also
                                                awsztrag, daz wir des darnach vertragen seyn, wan
                                                uns sölich sache niht wol füklich sein, als ir selbs
                                                wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> mugt. Denn wo
                                                wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb
                                                  <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                                  <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
